## Summary
This documentation covers the Setup and Targeting configuration for Amplitude Guides and Surveys, detailing user targeting options (All Users vs Targeted Users with property/cohort filtering), trigger conditions (element appearance/clicks, time delays, smart delay, rage click, user confusion, event tracking), page targeting rules, priority levels, display limits, status management (Draft/Published/Schedule), and active state behavior with tiebreaker logic for multiple eligible experiences.

